caption: This is amazing!!!  Fresh handmade tortillas. The tacos are so gooood. It’s like my mouth was dancing. Honestly Tacos al pastor are the king of the tacos! Staff are very friendly and nice 👍🏼. The salsa is extremely good to. Recommend the green one, it’s not even spicy. GO CHECK IT OUT!! YUMMMM!

Apparently this place had had other locations in nyc for a while now. I just discovered them walking through the market. After buying a slice of pizza from slice joint I was still hungry so as soon as I saw them I had to try it. And good thing I did because it was super delicious. So good that I had to tell the staff how great the al pastore taco was. I just wish that the taco wasn't $6. But it's definitely worth it to come back when my pockets are loaded. If flavor is any measure of success then this chain is going to be well-known throughout the country or definitely in the tri-state.
